headline: This Monster Dividend Growth Stock Is Up 50% So Far This Year
summary: Philip Morris International is seeing growing demand for its alternative nicotine products and is getting a boost from a depreciating dollar.  Philip Morris International (NYSE: PM) has gone straight up and to the right.  Philip Morris International's returns are a cumulation of bets made over the past 10 years.
